snippet.title: Infinite Seek and Find - Trailer
snippet.description:
Infinite Seek and Find is now available on:
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2511440/Infinite_Seek_and_Find/
Nintendo Switch US: https://bit.ly/4dV91ng
Nintendo Switch EU: https://bit.ly/46XFkzO

Welcome to your ultimate hidden object challenge. Infinite Seek and Find offers a wide selection of image sets and customizable difficulty level - from a basic level where only the size matters to the most hardcore challenge, where the colors can trick you.

- Over 10 image sets with different themes
- 3 preset difficulty modes and a possibility to set your own custom difficulty
- Images differing by size, rotation, reflection, and colors
